            <p>(c) Expedited Action Risks Where we choose to act on an urgent request, you authorise us and our approved consultants or support partners to proceed without standard checks or confirmations. You accept full responsibility for the outcome, including any errors, omissions, or unintended consequences, and release us from all liability in respect of such actions.</p>
